Introduction

SONOKI (also known as SOKO NO KIMINI) was a Korean live idol girl group under the LOUDCARNIVAL project. They made their official live debut with a concert on July 25, 2020, performing "Soko no Kimi ni". The group disbanded on July 3, 2022.
